{
  "stem": "21437.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The children that I played with-- where we lived there was-- there could have been about 50 families around because the-- the way the flats were built, it was that the yard was in the middle and on the side were the flats.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people lived, you know, all around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was only downstairs across from us one printer, one Jewish family who had a-- a-- who had a printing sort of business.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But all the rest were non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow to them, they keep telling me, oh, you are not like-- like a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I didn't-- I didn't take any notice because sort of we were still friendly, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We sort of liked each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was their friend then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But once I was outside walking the street, as I had to sometimes, by myself, as we were not driven to school, I didn't want to be-- I could have been not driven, but taken, by-- by horse-- by horses and-- and a buggy.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to be just like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't want to be different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, you know, that this will sort of allow me, really-- I wanted to be friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to make friends at school and things like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the only one in that particular school because they were very selective.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the next school, [POLISH] Pilsudskigo, there were three Jewish children in the whole school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just did not-- they try in a subtle way to-- to avoid explaining why not, but they really did not accept Jewish school-- Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they didn't really-- they did not pick when the teachers were around.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
